  "description": "Is a Product Feature that defines how financial transactions related to a banking product are recorded and booked in the banks accounting system.\r\n\r\nComment:\r\nThis feature governs the initial recording (booking) of financial events such as deposits, loan disbursements, fees, or interest in the banks financial system.\r\n\r\nIt ensures that every transaction generated by a product is properly recognized in the banks books according to accounting and regulatory rules.",
